info.description:
# Hello and welcome to Appeagles API! 
# 
## You can use this API to access all our API endpoints, such as:
## 
* Price
* Strategy
* Managed Listings
* Batch status


The API is organized around REST. Requests should be made over HTTPS. All request and response bodies, including errors, are formatted in JSON and encoded in UTF-8.
info.title: Appeagle API
